Build-Depends: debhelper (>=9)

Package: documaster-noark-extraction-validator
Architecture: any
Depends: openjdk-8-jdk
Description: Documaster Noark Extraction Validator
 Provides validating for Noark (5.x) extraction packages according to
 the requirements specified by the Noark 5 standard. The tool is a
 console application that:
 * parses a given extraction package;
 * stores its contents in a temporary in-memory (or file) database;
 * validates metadata and documents, and collects information.
 * generates a report that summarizes the results.
